  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Humanitarian Assistance for Refugees on Chios Island</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Activity 1: Apostoli will renovate existing sanitary facilities, including a 
shower unit for women, a shower unit for men, and toilets at 10 containers used as sleeping quarters. 

Activity 2: Apostoli will provide 5 portable showers: 2 shower units 
for women/children and 3 units for men.  

Activity 3: Apostoli will distribute up to 1,700 kits: 1,350 individual hygiene kits, 200 female hygiene kits, and 150 baby hygiene kits.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Project Goal: To improve living conditions of illegal immigrants at reception centers on Chios Island. 

Project Objective:  To improve individual and group hygiene by upgrading sanitary facilities and providing personal hygiene items to immigrants in Chios.</narrative>
  </description>
